music is alive and well everywhere weve been lately and weve 
been everywhere 
among the performers in attendance were waylon jennings bill 
monroe johnny rodriguez chet atkins mel mcdaniel and emmylou 
harris 
the exhibit to be displayed for two years includes photos 
posters films of cashs early performances costumes musical 
instruments and mementos of his career the exhibit is sponsored by 
the holiday corp of memphis 
