<TEXT>
sen paul simon calling himself an 
underdog fighting for the underdog says he hopes wisconsins 
progressive political tradition can carry him to victory in the 
states april 5 primary 
simon who won the democratic primary in his home state of 
illinois last week needs another victory to keep his candidacy 
