weather fire officials say it could be the sign of an early and 
dangerous fire season during the grim fire season last year 
lightningspawned blazes blackened nearly a million acres of mostly 
forest lands in california 
this is very similar to the weather pattern we saw last year 
at this time said maryn pitt assistant director of the state 
